description: Souvenirs of a wonderful afternoon's conversation with saxophone master Michael Hashim, who has been on the New York scene since the Seventies, and has observed and played with many of the legendary figures.  Recorded by Michael Steinman for JAZZ LIVES (http://www.jazzlives.wordpress.com).
